<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 10 (August 23, 2013)</h4><ul><li>The base damage of this Loadout's passive has been reduced to 5-14 (based on level) per stack, down from 5-18 (based on level) per stack.</li><li>The Power ratio on this Loadout's passive has been reduced to 0.03 per stack, down from 0.075 per stack.</li><li>This Loadout's passive, Resonance, now only applies to your primary target.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 8 (August 09, 2013)</h4><ul><li>The damage of this loadout has been reduced to 5-18 (depending on level) per stack, down from 8-21 per stack.</li><li>Fixed a bug where if two players with Resonance attacked the same target, only one instance of Resonance would do damage, but it would stack twice as fast.</li></ul>